#-  James Longstreet's§0
§0   §0
§0    Cocktail and Ale§0
§0      Recipe Guide
#- Triple K Special§0
§0
§0Ingredients:§0
§0
§0    1 shot vodka§0
§0    1 shot gin§0
§0    1 shot brandy§0
§0    Juice 2 lemons§0
§0    Juice 1 orange 
#- 
§0Mix the ingredients together in the cocktail shaker. Shake well and pour into a glass. Add diced orange followed by chunks of lemon. Top the glass with a slice of lime and finish with some mint leaves. 
#- 
§0Chocolate Friday§0
§0Ingredients:§0
§0
§0    1 shot whisky§0
§0    1 sprig of mintleaves§0
§0    Dash of milk§0
§0    1 bar of chocolate 
#- 
§0Mix the ingredients together in the cocktail shaker along with a crumbled chocolate bar. Shake well and pour into a glass. Warm it in an oven, then add fresh cream. Finally sprinkle with chocolate dust.
