#- Mix the ingredients together in the cocktail shaker. Shake well and pour into a glass. Add diced pineapple then top with fresh cream. 
#- Kike Blaster§0
§0
§0Ingredients:§0
§0
§0    Juice 1 pineapple§0
§0    Juice 1 orange§0
§0    Juice 1 lemon 
#- Mix the ingredients together in the cocktail shaker. Shake well and pour into a glass. Simply top with slices of fresh lemon and finish this light and refreshing mix.§0
§0Add one dollar bill.
#- Imitator Kike Blaster§0
§0
§0Ingredients:§0
§0
§0    1 shot vodka§0
§0    Juice 3 limes §0

#- Mix the ingredients together in the cocktail shaker. Shake well and pour into a glass. Add a sprinkling of mint leaves followed by a single lime slice to finish this classic.
#- Grand Wizard Blizzard§0
§0
§0Ingredients:§0
§0
§0    2 shots vodka§0
§0    1 shot gin§0
§0    Juice 1 orange§0
§0    Juice 1 lime§0
§0    Juice 1 lemon 
#- 
§0Mix the ingredients together in the cocktail shaker. Shake well and pour into a glass. Add pineapple chunks to the drink. Finally finish this magical concoction with slices of lime. 
#- The Trayvon Martini§0
§0
§0    1 shot vodka§0
